import React from 'react'; import './FAQ.css'; function FAQ() { return (

Frequently Asked Questions

General Questions

What are your opening hours?

We are open Monday to Friday from 9:00 AM to 9:00 PM and on weekends from 10:00 AM to 8:00 PM.

Do you offer vegan or gluten-free options?

Yes, we have a selection of vegan and gluten-free products available. Please check our menu for more details.

Ordering and Delivery

How can I place an order?

You can place an order through our website or by calling us at +1 (84) 546-6789.

Do you deliver?

Yes, we offer delivery services within a 10-mile radius of our bakery.

); } export default FAQ;
